data.description: Welcome Home! This 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom house offers a perfect blend of modern amenities and thoughtful upgrades.    Upgrades include solar panels with the potential for bills as low as $30, water filtration system, Adler Security and Ring Doorbell/Cameras. Outside there's a fire put and insulated outdoor shed with electricity, can be used as a home office, studio, or workshop. The inside boast new carpet and fresh paint. The seller will also provide professional home and carpet cleaning, new mini blinds, and toilet seats before closing.     Conveniently located just minutes away from Buckroe Beach, Mercury Blvd, shops, restaurants, and more. Don't miss the chance to make this house yours. Schedule a viewing today!    Use the preferred lender and receive $1,800 in lender credits. PRICE INCREASED. Seller will pay off solar panels at closing with a full-price offer.
